author: rekovic
body:
Fix: put dropped RPCTwinMux unpacker back into L1T unpacker sequence.

This unpacker is already in the L1REPACK:Full step relevant for HLT tests
and workflows. However, it was removed from the L1TRawToDigi sequence 
unintentionally.  It should be there.
title: Pr100x RPCTwinMux in L1TRawToDigi Sequence
